OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and fine
OL,6,Fthrough Thursday evening and remaining
OL,7,Flargely clear overnight into Friday.
OL,8,FSome cloud arriving overnight and
OL,9,Flikely turning misty with fog
OL,10,Fdeveloping in places, with some dense
OL,11,Fpatches.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FMisty start with some fog.
OL,14,FRemaining mild with early, hazy
OL,15,Fsunshine before becoming cloudier.
OL,16,FSome showery light rain arriving by
OL,17,Fafternoon, perhaps turning heavier and
OL,18,Fmore persistent by evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
