OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy and mild through the
OL,7,Fweekend and into Monday, with
OL,8,Fwidespread low cloud, some fog, and
OL,9,Fchance of rain at times.
